title: Muc-Off 8 in 1 Bicycle Cleaning Kit - Bike Cleaning Kit, Cleaning Bundle for MTB/Road/Gravel Bikes - Set Includes Bike Cleaner and Bike Protect, Black
features: THE ULTIMATE GIFT: Muc-Off bike cleaning kits make a perfect gift for any cycling fanatic. We’ve bundled together a selection of our best products to get you started with super easy bike maintenance – whether you're a weekend warrior or a dedicated shredder, there's a Muc-Off kit for you

CLEAN AND PROTECT: The 8 in 1 Bicycle Cleaning Kit contains some of our hardest hitters when it comes to keeping your ride looking factory fresh This gnarly bundle is loaded with our infamous pink Nano Tech Bike Cleaner to shred grime fast and a can of Bike Protect to give you that post-wash protective bling

BIKE CLEANING TOOLS: To make your post-shred clean up even easier, we've packed this kit with a few of our handiest cleaning tools so that you can give your bike some serious TLC. The 8 in 1 Kit includes four of our best bike cleaning brushes and a nifty expanding sponge.

STORAGE TUB: This bike kit comes neatly packed into it's own storage tub. Fill it with warm water to clean your bike or soak your greasy parts and then use it to keep your cleaning kit tidy when you're finished

SUITABLE FOR ALL TYPES OF BIKE: Whether you prefer to hit the road or shred the trails on your MTB, our bicycle cleaning kits are suitable for use on all bikes. Our comprehensive product range has been designed to look after all two-wheeled toys
